    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
一筆啓上仕候。<lb />
然ニ先日御<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">直</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（じきに）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>申上置候二件の御決<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">儀</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（議）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>、何卒明朝より夜にかけ拝承仕度。<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">将</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（はた）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>、芸州士官の者共も京師の急ニ心せき、出帆の日を相尋られ居申候。彼是の所御察被<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>遣候。<lb />
早<seg facs="../../../gaiji/1-02/1-02-22.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(二の字点、1-2-22)" />御決の上、出帆の期御命相願候。誠恐謹言。<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">九月廿七日<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">直柔</seg></seg>
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em">本山先生</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_7" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 7em">左右</seg>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</seg></p></body>
